
---------------------------------------
TYPES OF INTENTS
---------------------------------------

1️⃣ EXPLICIT INTENT
- Target component is known
- Used inside the same app
- Example: Move from MainActivity to SecondActivity

2️⃣ IMPLICIT INTENT
- Target component is NOT known
- Android decides which app can handle it
- Example: Open Dialer, Browser, Share text

---------------------------------------
COMPARISON
---------------------------------------

EXPLICIT INTENT
✔ Used within app
✔ Faster
✔ More control

IMPLICIT INTENT
✔ Used for system apps
✔ Flexible
✔ Depends on user choice

